$ Excel: Power Pivot
@ Power Pivot

Power Pivot extends → development/databases/SQL-Server/Analysis-Services[Microsoft Analysis Services].

The primary language of Power Pivot is *DAX* (Data Analysis Expression), but → development/Data can also be queried with → development/Data/OLAP/MDX.

If Power Pivot is used to crunch large amounts of → development/Data, a → Microsoft/Office/32-vs-64-bit[64-bit installation of Excel] is needed if more than 2 GB of memory is needed by the
*SSAS Vertipaq Engine*.

sa:
 ? → Microsoft/products/Power/BI/Desktop is similar to Power Pivot but does not need an Excel installation.
